    <h2>Quake Live Console Commands</h2>

    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>Important:</strong> In Quake Live, setting an arbitrary <code>com_maxfps</code> value does not reliably produce that exact FPS. The engine tends to run at common frame-time steps, so "in-between" values can snap/round to a different effective FPS.<br/><br/>
