    <h2>üîß Troubleshooting: Stuck at 142 FPS?</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">142 FPS is a common Quake-engine FPS step. If you're stuck around 142 (or 166), it usually means you're being capped somewhere (or your chosen FPS value snapped to an engine step) ‚Äî not that your monitor is "142 Hz".</p>

